events.name: EV002アクティナの巫女からの依頼1-5

parameters:
Clea: There's no one here... Could it be that everyone has
already gone outside?

Mage Relm: That's not possible! There's no way they could
have broken through that seal, and besides...

Mage Relm: The murky liquid in front of us... It's like a
sinister swamp of magical power that has been boiled down to
its essence.

Priestess Sophia: Ankos is here... It would be wise to
think so.
??? 'Welcome, I'm here to welcome all of you.'

Demon Bride Ankos: Pathetic and pitiful, isn't it? A
hideous form where only the soul is sealed within a
crystal.

Demon Bride Ankos: This is the result of the hideous witch
demon Amedor, who shook the empire, becoming a bride. This
is how it looks.

Clea: I have received a request from the priestess of
Aktina. I will undertake the subjugation for the sake of
mourning the people of this village.

Demon Bride Ankos: Kukuku, ahahaha! Whether you call
yourself a priestess or not, you're just a little girl in
the end!

Demon Bride Ankos: Not only did you go through the trouble
of releasing the seal, but you even sent me four vessels for
my [soul]. How generous!

Demon Bride Ankos: I particularly like the daughter of the
beastmen... If your body and my soul are merged, we will be
closer to achieving our long-cherished desire!
Demon Bride Ankos: Now, I shall dominate all of you!

Demon Bride Ankos: Ah... Shattered... Broken... I shall
live for eternity... Everything... for Lord Amedor...

Thief Nora: I-Is this enough?! You won't come after me
anymore, right?!

Mage Relm: The abnormal magical power has disappeared. This
place should be sealed as it was before.

Priestess Sophia: If Ankos hadn't been defeated, important
people would have been in trouble, you know.
Mage Relm: Isn't that a bit too sarcastic?

Priestess Sophia: Hehehe, I wonder if I drank too much
wine?
Clea: Let's go report that the mission has been completed.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
実績 裂けて砕けて割れて散る

Demon Bride Ankos: The quality of the empire's warriors has
declined. Although, the quality as vessels is top-notch.
Thief Nora: Ugh... I don't want to...
Demon Bride Ankos: Well then, shall we have our meal?

Demon Bride Ankos: As a meal, you were top-notch, huh?
Don't be sad, your soul will also disappear!

Thief Nora: Ngh... Stop it! What are you... Ahh, let
go...!
Thief Nora: N-No way! I-I, ah, w-ah, I...!
Thief Nora: I... I, me... myself...

Thief Nora: Your body belongs to me... Your soul... to my
magic... Kukuku...

Thief Nora: Hahaha, splendid! I'm looking forward to when I
completely blend in!
Thief Nora: Well, you guys... come over here.
後order：アダルトシーン「851」再生
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
後order：アダルトシーン「851」再生

Demon Bride Ankos: I've gotten quite used to it, but I'm
still far from my prime magical power...

Demon Bride Ankos: Shall I enter the empire and casually
procure a magician or something?
Bard: Oh, you're starting to look familiar.

Demon Bride Ankos: 'Oh, I see, we're acquainted.
Unfortunately, your acquaintances now belong to me.'
Demon Bride Ankos: And you will also become mine!
